<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Happy Anniversary, <%= userName %>!</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9fc;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 650px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 14px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f4b400, #ff9900);
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        color: #fff;
      }
      .header img {
        width: 120px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }
      .header p {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 35px 40px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .content h2 {
        color: #444;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .ribbon {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }
      .ribbon img {
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        object-fit: contain;
        animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }
      @keyframes float {
        0% {
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateY(-6px);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }
      .cta {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .cta a {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #f4b400;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(244, 180, 0, 0.4);
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 25px 20px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777;
        background: #f5f6f8;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #f4b400;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="Company Logo" />
        <h1>Happy Anniversary, <%= userName %>! üéä</h1>
        <p>Celebrating your journey with <%= companyName %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Dear <%= userName %>,</h2>
        <p>
          Today marks another milestone in our journey together, and we couldn‚Äôt
          be happier to celebrate it with you.
        </p>
        <p>
          On behalf of the entire <strong><%= companyName %></strong> family, we
          sincerely thank you for your continued trust, loyalty, and
          partnership. Working with clients like you inspires us to do our best
          every day.
        </p>

        <div class="ribbon">
          <img
            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/7010/7010852.png"
            alt="Anniversary Ribbon"
          />
        </div>

        <p
          style="
            text-align: center;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
            margin: 20px 0;
          "
        >
          ‚ÄúHere‚Äôs to more years of growth, innovation, and success ‚Äî together.‚Äù
        </p>

        <div class="cta">
          <a href="<%= ctaUrl %>" target="_blank">Visit Us ‚ù§Ô∏è</a>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 35px; font-size: 14px; color: #777">
          With heartfelt gratitude,<br />
          <strong>The <%= companyName %> Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= companyName %>. All rights
        reserved.<br />
        <a href="<%= appUrl %>"><%= appUrl %></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
